data.text: @emartinac I don’t use Instagram how it’s intended to be used I don’t think. I just post pictures. There’s so much happening there it can be overstimulating. ANYWAY. Im just going to randomly throw out baby names to you like I did to my coworker who rudely did not name her baby Godzilla.

@emartinac Okay so somehow I missed that you were expecting (CONGRATULATIONS!!!) but I was actually wondering to myself if you were planning on having babies. How exciting! Also I LOVE picking out names so let me know if you need any help there. I’ve always wanted to be a baby namer.
@emartinac Haha. Fair. Let me know what you’re wanting!
